titocc.compiler

Class Compiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • titocc.compiler.Compiler

  • public class Compiler
extends java.lang.Object
    Main compiler class. Accepts either a C source file or parser output (TranslationUnit object) as input and produces assembly code. The main compilation work is done in the code element classes, and Compiler class just works as a wrapper and initializes some necessary variables.
